text: James Templer (born 8 January 1936) is a British equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:British male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Great Britain Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
